---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="p-8 text-center bg-gray-50 font-sans flex flex-col items-center">
        <a href="/" class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition">
            <img src="/logo.png" alt="Goaly Logo" class="h-10 w-auto" />
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-teal-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text tracking-tight font-bold text-2xl">Goaly</span>
        </a>
		<div class="max-w-3xl w-full bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Privacy Policy for Goaly</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 21, 2026</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Welcome to Goaly. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. Our privacy policy is very simple and transparent.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">1. No Data Storage</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We do not store, retain, or share any of your personal data.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">2. No Analytics or Tracking</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Goaly does not use any analytics, third-party tracking, or behavior monitoring tools. Your use of the application is completely private.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">3. How We Handle Your Session and Calendar</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">To provide our service, we only perform the following actions:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Session Management:</strong> We maintain your active session so you can stay logged in.</li>
                <li><strong>Calendar Integration:</strong> We act strictly on your behalf to set and manage goal-related events directly on your personal calendar (e.g., Google Calendar).</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We do not copy or save your calendar events to any external database. All calendar data remains securely between your device and your calendar provider.</p>

            <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />
            <p class="text-gray-700">If you have any questions about our privacy practices, please feel free to contact us on <a href="https://github.com/gandazgul/goaly/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Github</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
